cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of blockchain and DLTs to combat fake news, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR). It also involves the use of technology to store and secure information (cs.SI), as well as the analysis and detection of information (cs.IR). The paper also touches on the economic impact of fake news (cs.CY) and the potential use of multimedia (cs.MM) to spread misinformation.
